track_notes: Large parking place at ski lift and Lajnar restorant. Easy path along the non steep ski slope and then along the new path to the old pre WW2 barracks, which is now a shepherds hut. The summit is close to the hut, Lot of spase for antennas. About 60 minutes easy walk
track_title: New track to the summit from Soriska planina

track_notes: Short and easy route to Slatnik
